tail: start by stirring together chicken stock base, garlic, dried rosemary, ground sage, and black pepper in a small bowl. Then, layer shredded cooked chicken, spiralized zucchini, shredded carrot, thinly sliced celery, and finely chopped sweet onion in a jar. When ready to eat, pour hot water over the ingredients in the jar, cover, and let it sit for a few minutes before stirring and enjoying.
